mountains eastspine "The Broken Spine" : ridge (1030,618) (1185,706) (1345,795) width=70mi
mountains spur "The Vakh Teeth" : ridge (170,120) (290,180) (410,150) width=45mi
; the drowned crest - the elvish archipelago, colinear with both spines
